OL,3,CBody set up to investigate Troubles
OL,4,Ccases to probe 1974 Guildford pub
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FOne of the first investigations
OL,8,Fcarried out by a new body tasked with
OL,9,Fprobing outstanding cases from the
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland Troubles will be into
OL,11,Fthe 1974 Guildford pub bombings.
OL,13,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,14,FReconciliation and Information (ICRIR)
OL,15,Fhas registered 85 inquiries since
OL,16,Fbecoming operational earlier this year.
OL,18,FIts head, former Lord Chief Justice
OL,19,FSir Declan Morgan has confirmed first
OL,20,Freports will likely be delivered in
OL,21,Fthe first half of next year.
