OL,3,CBody set up to investigate Troubles
OL,4,Ccases to probe 1974 Guildford pub
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FThe organisation has confirmed it has
OL,8,Faccepted a request to investigate the
OL,9,Fatrocity in which four soldiers and a
OL,10,Fcivilian were killed in a blast at the
OL,11,FHorse and Groom pub in Guildford,
OL,12,FSurrey, on October 5 1974.
OL,14,FAnother bomb detonated 30 minutes
OL,15,Flater at the Seven Stars.
OL,17,FThe Guildford Four and Maguire Seven
OL,18,Fwere wrongly convicted of the attacks
OL,19,Fin one of the UK's biggest
OL,20,Fmiscarriages of justice.
