OL,3,CBody set up to investigate Troubles
OL,4,Ccases to probe 1974 Guildford pub
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FAn IRA terror cell later claimed
OL,8,Fresponsibility.
OL,10,FThe ICRIR was created by the
OL,11,FConservative government's
OL,12,Fcontroversial Legacy Act which halted
OL,13,Fscores of civil cases and inquests
OL,14,Finto Troubles deaths.
OL,16,FBereaved families, victims and certain
OL,17,Fpublic authorities can instead request
OL,18,Fthe ICRIR carry out an investigation.
