OL,3,CBody set up to investigate Troubles
OL,4,Ccases to probe 1974 Guildford pub
OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,FHowever, opposition to the new
OL,8,Fcommission led to protests and claims
OL,9,Fthat access to justice had been shut
OL,10,Fdown.
OL,12,FThe ICRIR announced on Monday that,
OL,13,Fsince becoming operational in May, it
OL,14,Fhas registered 85 inquiries from
OL,15,Fvictims, survivors and families about
OL,16,Fthe possibility of an investigation
OL,17,Finto their injury or the death of a
OL,18,Floved one.
