OL,7,FIn an update to its work, the ICRIR
OL,8,Falso confirmed that, of those
OL,9,Finquiries, eight have been accepted
OL,10,Ffor investigation and are in the
OL,11,Finformation recovery stage.
OL,13,FThe body is led by retired judge Sir
OL,14,FDeclan Morgan, a former lord chief
OL,15,Fjustice for Northern Ireland.
