OL,7,FThe Chief Commissioner said the update
OL,8,F"reflects the commission's values
OL,9,Fabout being open and accountable, and
OL,10,Fabove all the focus on delivering for
OL,11,Fthose who have come to the commission
OL,12,Fseeking answers".
OL,14,FSir Declan said all at the commission
OL,15,Fare committed to following the
OL,16,Fapproach the design framework sets out
OL,17,Fso the body meets what it has promised.
