OL,7,F"We are now at a stage where people
OL,8,Fhave come forward and put their trust
OL,9,Fin the commission to take their
OL,10,Frequests forward. We will now do so in
OL,11,Fline with our values and core
OL,12,Fprinciples," he said.
OL,14,F"We are moving into the next phase of
OL,15,Four work as the serious and important
OL,16,Ftask of investigation begins.
