OL,7,F"In doing this we must meet the
OL,8,Fcommitments that we have made to each
OL,9,Fperson who comes to us, through our
OL,10,Fopen and published policies, and
OL,11,Fthrough our trauma and resiliency
OL,12,Finformed model."
OL,14,FCommissioner for investigations Peter
OL,15,FSheridan said: "Many of the
OL,16,Findividuals and families that the
OL,17,Fcommission will meet will have
OL,18,Fexperienced harm and suffering and may
OL,19,Fhave waited many years to find out
OL,20,Fmore about what they and their loved
OL,21,Fones went through.
